snippet.title: Infamous Crime Locations
snippet.description: If you like crime shows then my channel is perfect for you. I don't just talk about different crimes and crime locations but actually go and find them and visit them for you. Infamous Crime Locations is hosted by Harmin (Formerly Harmin vlogs) and will take you to crime scene locations twice a week on mondays and fridays. Make sure to hit subscribe. More crime scene locations are always around the corner.
